structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS
COUNTY GOVERNMENT (FISCAL COURTS AND COUNTY COMMISSIONERS)

law.history: Repealed 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 228, sec. 19, effective June 17, 1978; amended ch. 384, sec. 145. -- Amended 1976 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 14, sec. 50. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 938f-2.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Jailer relieved of duties as to courts in certain counties having cities of second class.
